elisa3_firmware_advanced-master
folder has files required to program the elisa 3 robots, main.c is the file that will mostly controll robot functionality depending on the switch inside the robot
this is for programming each robot independently

How to program Elisa.txt has detailed information on how to program the robots.

Python_for_Elisa3_Radio_control
folder has files that can send control elisas with radio signals from computer with elisa usb

elisa3_remote_library-master
folder has an implementation of controlling the robots using C code from the computing using the radio signal
This has not been fully implemented




